messages.message: What kind of test is this from?
The thing to make sure you hit home on is, Abby is no longer a competitor. They have lost. They won’t be around in 5-10 years because they have not adapted and improved.

No one talks about Abby in the same league as Microsoft, Google, or Amazon. They are great at PDF’s and amzingly high quality documents. The moment you step into normal documents they are dead in the water. They are going to be wiped out and forgotten as a company.
